1 or s ervices that include subjective standards if such standards are
2 fully disclosed and explained to any potential customer or investor
3 prior to entering into a contract for such investment, product, or
4 service.
5 D. A credit union that violates the provisions of this section
6 shall be subject to a civil penalty of Fifty Thousand Dollars
